<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>We've Received Your Inquiry</title>

<style>

*{
margin:0;
padding:0;
box-sizing:border-box;
}

body{
background:#f4f7fb;
font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,"Segoe UI",Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;
padding:40px 15px;
color:#1f2937;
}

.container{
max-width:620px;
margin:auto;
background:#ffffff;
border-radius:20px;
overflow:hidden;
box-shadow:0 20px 50px rgba(15,23,42,.10);
}

.header{
background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0f172a,#1e3a8a,#2563eb);
padding:48px 32px;
text-align:center;
color:#ffffff;
}

.logo{
display:inline-block;
padding:10px 18px;
border-radius:999px;
border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.2);
background:rgba(255,255,255,.08);
font-size:12px;
font-weight:700;
letter-spacing:2px;
text-transform:uppercase;
margin-bottom:22px;
}

.header h1{
font-size:30px;
font-weight:700;
margin-bottom:12px;
}

.header p{
font-size:16px;
line-height:28px;
opacity:.92;
}

.content{
padding:40px 36px;
}

.message{
font-size:16px;
line-height:30px;
color:#475569;
margin-bottom:28px;
}

.card{
background:#f8fafc;
border:1px solid #e2e8f0;
border-radius:16px;
padding:24px;
text-align:center;
margin-bottom:30px;
}

.card h2{
font-size:18px;
color:#2563eb;
margin-bottom:12px;
}

.card p{
font-size:15px;
line-height:28px;
color:#64748b;
}

.email{
display:inline-block;
margin-top:16px;
padding:12px 18px;
background:#ffffff;
border:1px solid #dbeafe;
border-radius:10px;
font-weight:600;
color:#0f172a;
word-break:break-all;
}

.signature{
font-size:16px;
line-height:30px;
color:#374151;
}

.footer{
padding:28px;
text-align:center;
background:#f8fafc;
border-top:1px solid #e5e7eb;
font-size:13px;
line-height:24px;
color:#64748b;
}

.footer strong{
color:#111827;
}

@media(max-width:640px){

.header{
padding:40px 24px;
}

.header h1{
font-size:26px;
}

.content{
padding:28px 22px;
}

}

</style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="container">

<div class="header">

<div class="logo">
TECH SQUARE NEST
</div>

<h1>Inquiry Received</h1>

<p>
Thank you for contacting Tech Square Nest.
</p>

</div>

<div class="content">

<div class="message">

We've successfully received your inquiry and appreciate your interest in working with us.

Our team will carefully review your request and get back to you as soon as possible, typically within one business day.

</div>

<div class="card">

<h2>Confirmation</h2>

<p>
This acknowledgement has been sent to:
</p>

<div class="email">
<%= email %>
</div>

</div>

<div class="signature">

Thank you for considering <strong>Tech Square Nest</strong>.

We look forward to connecting with you soon.

</div>

</div>

<div class="footer">

<strong>Tech Square Nest</strong><br>

Building Modern Software, AI Solutions & Digital Experiences.

<br><br>

This is an automated acknowledgement email. Please do not reply to this message.

</div>

</div>

</body>
</html>